cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with statistical machine translation and linguistic resources. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as these fields are closely related to machine translation. Additionally, it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the paper discusses how to improve translation quality when limited parallel corpora is available. Finally, it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as neural machine translation is a popular approach in machine translation research.
